Date: 1999-05-28

Title: Bosonization of quantum sine-Gordon field with a boundary

Authors: Bo-yu Hou, Kang-jie Shi, Yan-shen Wang and Wen-li Yang

Comments: Latex 25pages

Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A12 (1997) 1711-1741

Boundary operators and boundary ground states in sine-Gordon model with afixed boundary condition are studied using bosonization and q-deformedoscillators.We also obtain the form-factors of this model.